title: Munsbach railway station
text:
Munsbach railway station (, , ) is a <a href="railway%20station">railway station</a> serving <a href="Munsbach">Munsbach</a>, in the <a href="Communes%20of%20Luxembourg">commune</a> of <a href="Schuttrange">Schuttrange</a>, in southern <a href="Luxembourg">Luxembourg</a>. It is operated by <a href="Chemins%20de%20Fer%20Luxembourgeois">Chemins de Fer Luxembourgeois</a>, the <a href="public%20ownership">state-owned</a> railway company.
The station is situated on <a href="CFL%20Line%2030">Line 30</a>, which connects Luxembourg City to the east of the country and <a href="Trier">Trier</a>.
